summary: People are already complaining about how Sophie Turner looks too bored in the Dark Phoenix trailer just like how people...
body:
People are already complaining about how Sophie Turner looks too bored in the Dark Phoenix trailer just like how people complained that Brie Larson looked too bored in her Captain Marvel trailer.

Ya’ll do realize that it’s intentional, right?

The Phoenix is an emotionless cosmic being that is practically taking over Jean Grey and consuming her humanity. Of course Jean is going to slowly become more and more apathetic under the influence of the Dark Phoenix.

Also, did ya’ll just ignore that shot of her having a breakdown in the rain?

Meanwhile, Captain Marvel’s Kree half is explained to be emotionless and it’ll be a key theme in the film because her Kree half wars with her humanity.

Smh, ya’ll don’t ever bother to think that there’s a specific reason why these female characters look “bored”? That there’s a narrative reason for their apathy?
